title: possible cognitive effects
comment: The cognitive effects is at this point unknown and ergo ambivalent. Would having a more healthy sleep cycle cause cognitive health? Or would messing with natural sleep cause an unhealthy cognitive health effect?

title: possible mental effects
comment: it's unknown whether or not effecting your sleep cycle would have a positive effect (due to managing to sleep easier or at better times) or negatively (by effecting the natural sleep cycle). It could also effect how information is processed and retained leading to a potential increase in trauma.
